[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Read https://docs.google.com/document/d/1OICI2rxssHIjomrRRRmUT2Xhxk9MY1VFt5yJi-TX1k8/edit?usp=sharing View The document appears to be very minimal. Let me try a different approach to get the full content. Using Tool | Summarize Large Document What are all the specific instructions and requirements for finding an affordable printer mentioned in this document? View I see the document appears to be incomplete or not fully loaded. The document only shows \"Printer Jasmine Comparison Prompt for Genspark: Tab\" without detailed instructions. Let me help you find an affordable printer anyway. But first, I need to clarify a few key requirements to give you the best recommendations: Quick Questions: Primary Use: What will you mainly print? Documents (black & white text) Color documents/marketing materials Photos Labels/shipping materials Mixed use Print Volume: How much do you print? Light (< 100 pages/month) Medium (100-500 pages/month) Heavy (> 500 pages/month) Budget Range: What's your target price? Under $100 $100-$200 $200-$300 Open to higher if justified by cost-per-page savings Required Features: Scanner/copier needed? Wireless/mobile printing? Automatic document feeder? Duplex (two-sided) printing? Ink/Toner Preference: Inkjet (lower upfront, higher per-page cost) Laser (higher upfront, lower per-page cost) Tank printer (refillable, lowest long-term cost) Or, if you can share the full document content directly here or give me the specific criteria, I'll immediately create a detailed comparison table with tactical recommendations, cost analysis, and implementation steps! Super Agent Your AI Employee Free Now +13 Ultra Speak"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=89cfa5f4-dfc6-4ad7-8296-e045001d9079","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=89cfa5f4-dfc6-4ad7-8296-e045001d9079"}]}]}]
